| name             = Antisthenes
| birth_date       = c. 445 BC
| birth_place      = Athens
| death_date       = c. 365 BC (aged approx. 80)
| death_place      = Athens
| school_tradition = [[Cynicism (philosophy)|Cynicism]]
| main_interests   = [[Asceticism]], [[ethics]], [[language]], [[literature]], [[logic]]
| notable_ideas    = Laying the foundations of [[Cynicism (philosophy)|Cynic]] philosophy<br>Distinction between [[sense and reference]]
